        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-num">08</div>
          <div>
            <div class="faq-q">Can I qualify if my personal and business banking are commingled?</div>
            <div class="faq-a">Yes but more complex. Bank-statement Non-QM works cleanest with separated personal and business accounts. For commingled accounts, the underwriter must identify business deposits within the personal account &mdash; possible but requires more documentation overhead. We recommend establishing separated business banking now if not already in place; the qualifying picture is dramatically cleaner with separated accounts.</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-num">09</div>
          <div>
